@TodoMiniAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

GET {{TodoMiniAPI_HostAddress}}/todoitems/
Accept: application/json

###Replace {id}
GET {{TodoMiniAPI_HostAddress}}/todoitems/{id}
Accept: application/json

